rows.label: qst104501_msg0001
rows.name:
Sniff-sniff, sniff-sniff...
Friend have smell of strong fighter!
Is friend very strong?

rows.label: qst104501_msg0002
rows.name:
Sorry... Snififi should not sniff-sniff
friends before even say hello.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0003
rows.name:
Snififi have very good nose. Never make
any mistake with smell before!

rows.label: qst104501_msg0004
rows.name:
And nose of Snififi say, Snififi should
open new shop in Temperantia!

rows.label: qst104501_msg0005
rows.name:
But nobody have shop there yet.
So Snififi not know of good travel route.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0006
rows.name:
Snififi think nose alone probably not
enough to keep fellow merchant safe.

rows.label: qst104501_msg0007
rows.name:
So was sniffing around to find strong
person to use as bodyguard!

rows.label: qst104501_msg0008
rows.name:
Snififi sniff-sniff 100 people, and
you smell strongest out of all 100!

rows.label: qst104501_msg0009
rows.name:
Please, friend! Help Snififi set up
shop in Temperantia!

rows.label: qst104501_msg0011
rows.name:
Snififi will wait on Overlook Hill
in Temperantia then! Come quick!
